      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOLLOWTHEACE (2) was a big improver here second up when he led from a wider barrier than this and went on to score by 3m. Has the speed to take advantage of this barrier and hasn't missed a place at this shorter distance. Goes very well third-up with two wins and a placing from three attempts so should be peaking. METEOR MOTH (8) has had to work in both outings since getting close to the smart Hi Manameisjeff at Listed level here last month. Strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance and draws for a trail. ALWAYS BE BLAKEY (1) has come from the back row for a win and a placing in two starts here since a spell and is well served by the ace draw. DESSIE GEE (6) has claims off a win here three back.",
